  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-25ddb3d6-5614-4df6-82bf-cdeb947aae98\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223073085794/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-55b67ac9-b86d-42ab-b7d4-f233cf01c1a9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223073085794/001.jpeg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-21660eef-6a68-4dab-b5ba-516a91f5b87f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223073085794/002.JPG\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2d808ba8-e749-48a8-883e-d2c1e926c1ad\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223073085794/003.JPG\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-aad96d30-81d2-49e8-952c-8beae0d6e41f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-436e7e02-2cc1-4ef5-98d6-29df66b4ef18\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f5e6611c-8a91-4c75-a390-cae20b6c3f52\" style=\"color:#555555;\">여러분은 일회용 컵의 환경문제에 대해 어렴풋이 들어보셨을 거라고 생각됩니다. 2017년 자연순환사회연대의 자료에 따르면 우리가 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a6f32c1b-7440-43c2-83cd-7ee216f02c59\" style=\"color:#ff008c;\"><b>매일 사용하는 테이크아웃 컵은 230억 개 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-d02ea5eb-c595-4a28-9b0e-82d9aba15a43\" style=\"color:#555555;\">정도입니다. 그중에 재활용되는 것은 전체의 1.4%인 약 3억 2천만 개입니다. 아직까지 이러한 재활용 빈도가 높지 않은 이유는 우리가 재활용(Recycle)을 거쳐 재사용(Re-usable)이 되는 과정에서의 효율성이 크게 기대에 미치지 못하기 때문입니다. 이 문제를 해결해 나가기 위해서는 효율의 문제만을 고려하는 것이 아니라 환경과 시민 공감 등의 방향에서 서로의 노력이 필요하다고 할 수 있겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8e80b0e5-ec72-4731-af40-d5e4360d2043\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-ff9267bf-fdd5-40b1-b6a5-e9b4ea2a904d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_bubble\" id=\"SE-3c3be445-fde4-435c-89f4-560648dbdb42\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_bubble\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f59c7ae2-c5cf-4db8-a0a8-6c43ef9bb5eb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-3c2cb7e6-f533-4e63-976e-b784f17ea2a4\" style=\"\"><b>그러나 가장 중요한 것은 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f94920a8-f1b2-4471-842f-1b9a4da95453\" style=\"color:#00b976;\"><b>우리 아이들의 미래 환경을 위해</b></span><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-067309aa-a7a3-4932-aef1-807e4f3628bd\" style=\"\"><b>서라면 지금부터라도 조금씩 바꿔 나가야 하는 노력을 해야 한다는 것입니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cc747b80-086f-4815-a61d-df5945676caa\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a86e9c9d-657f-4545-9490-5edf07cad23a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-2c49ae49-057a-4cb2-8317-da0409a29457\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오늘은 앞으로 현실로 다가온 다회용 컵의 효능과 그 활용가치에 대해 논의해 보겠습니다. 이 글의 결론부터 말씀드리자면 미래를 대비하는 자세가 여러분의 사업에 도움이 되는 방향으로 전개될 것이기에 끝까지 함께해 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9ee1f810-3b2a-42e7-90b7-6635410a555e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5670eef3-9c35-43ae-a1d2-496a1908c3ba\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0a7a4808-4fd8-43a4-9eeb-445288997371\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5393a19b-9d76-46f4-a7a7-33a62240ac47\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1231aafe-1ddb-41ac-9d79-559b25f9bc22\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>환경 오염은 치료가 불가능한 질병입니다. 그것은 단지 예방할 수 있습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-cite\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f8c6b03f-8ab0-4799-b71e-024272489f39\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-ab9ba5d0-9374-4c43-9ae4-3d9a9e56f551\" style=\"\">- Barry Commoner-</span></p></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-603522a8-6a43-4929-9ed8-ccfcaceef8fb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fa9d9af3-f16e-4b92-8ffb-e25190b61152\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9e8ff7c8-a1d7-461f-af01-976fbfc41380\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9d70d373-0926-4a58-a8e3-c0e125a77bfb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">승화피앤피(주)에서는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f1a9630d-eb39-4a48-b0ca-8a37ec37a944\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a8e44682-b398-495b-bafc-ea57a96c29f2\" style=\"color:#00b976;\"><b>세 가지의 장점을 살린 다회용 컵을 제작해 드립니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-40c8eacb-6884-40d0-81bb-b77dd8064658\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:500px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223073085794/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8cffd710-d78b-4e9a-b7c3-b4f9e970dec3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-9616d963-8a20-49f2-a4e0-b8e266ce81d2\" style=\"\">e-몰드컵 로고</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-de7f6033-e7fe-4ea9-a4e4-02c4aec214c0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\" style=\"max-width:202px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223073085794/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e0ac3d4f-7298-46ca-8e65-f93648119197\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-788136ff-84f0-41a0-a35a-141452035ed1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-43dc4755-4c71-4a0d-be78-28644ee18a78\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-775b9781-9502-489f-8e87-ac35063dbdc4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223073085794/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f11bee54-661b-4c1d-b00a-35227d3befbb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9c60f5fb-d245-472d-aa19-c3d45f613341\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>Made in KOREA가 중요합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7a8cf592-2e41-4f7f-a3eb-9a72cc947a8c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dbb19164-1eda-4e59-b30f-2ba76427a1b7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">믿을 수 있는 우리나라 제품이어야 합니다. 그중에서도 체계적인 공정과 철저한 품질관리로 가장 최상의 제품만을 고집하는 승화피앤피(주)의 제품을 경험해 보십시오. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-8f3849f1-a5ad-45ce-9411-c5ec4fc3eb26\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>국내 자체 생산설비는 물론 수년간 계속해온 연구개발로 친환경 연구 과제를 우수한 사례로 수행</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4cf10e33-8081-4dea-9a9a-83d4c81f5a96\" style=\"color:#555555;\">해 왔으며 국내 특허는 물론 국제 공인 자격기준 심사까지 모두 통과한 제품을 경험하실 수 있으실 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2cf490d1-e182-47d9-b018-8839198d592d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8857dbb7-02e7-4572-ab35-d58e5729af43\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-efa6e7da-933b-4793-85e4-0ce8eed14b06\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-00c19b5b-3cae-4c7d-8eac-f9a62f61704a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:722px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223073085794/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d701e023-5ffc-4493-b8df-e14663f3022c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2ee97d1b-bea4-4dea-8dc9-b9ee4a9c4960\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8b6a6ff0-bc02-499d-a85c-ebe10b0563d8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bd40f713-180e-46f6-a658-69c350c7cdb4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d875b8d8-b7c4-4bdb-95b3-52ca50a88eae\" style=\"color:#555555;\">환경호르몬을 전혀 포함하지 않고 있는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f107eff5-8a53-4eac-a2d5-cf6da710e499\" style=\"color:#00b976;\"><b>BPA FREE 제품</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-313d8f7f-33af-4205-9674-ee93fd385143\" style=\"color:#555555;\">으로 인체에 무해한 가장 안전한 제품입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f08e26cd-6c6e-4585-8c77-839f087daf86\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6356eefe-34ee-4792-b839-dccf6c41d4f8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-044d2fef-c92a-43f6-9f47-27d1fdc396b9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3538e5bf-0f6b-4fb7-b1c1-6fe3f971a277\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-916dd3af-a849-4197-b62b-d8ace2aaf2df\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-56274ff3-81e6-4091-9d67-704df5842117\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 FSSC22000, ISO 14001, ISO 9001 등 식품안전 경영시스템 인증을 통한 우수한 관리 시스템으로 제조단계별 이물 제어장치를 한 단계 업그레이드한 자체 생산공정을 보유하고 있습니다. 이는 외부와 차단된 인라인 생산방식이므로 조금 더 깨끗하고 안전한 생산제품을 만드는데 주력하고 있습니다. 또한 2017년부터 시작된 연구개발과 시설투자로 하루 생산량 10만 개 이상의 높은 생산력과 검증된 퀄리티로 최고의 제품만을 고집하는 그 비결이 모든 생산공 정안에 고스란히 담겨 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8a1f8a4b-2a29-4e45-b013-4704050580a0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2bf70661-3191-4cb3-839e-25d7e2c40b39\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-20c4f3fb-5c67-41c1-872b-5a3257e4ee5e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223073085794/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b23748c9-a6c7-48a1-8099-3b0b70aac5e4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-39efabd4-152b-4253-8422-87776428c31a\" style=\"\">각종 특허</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-de37e6ea-e6b0-416f-8fb8-1c61d9cb87ee\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:202px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223073085794/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-906047fe-d1cb-4c97-a55a-d13214aaaf4a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-49342526-f04c-4884-b764-c916b84eb964\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1431c8f6-cfe9-4d5f-8873-9a288604c1c0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-532519ba-4f78-4833-81a0-81649355d4e5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223073085794/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3621db93-9eb9-41ba-9359-1947a64b23de\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-920fbd33-220b-4f40-b212-7c16fb0a8473\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>다양한 사이즈는 물론 여러 장점이 함께합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ba1f6694-8973-4794-884c-706063ac9b40\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-da9dfbb9-6710-4921-83cd-88efa07df4d2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자체적으로 생산 시설을 보유하여야만 다양한 사이즈와 막대한 생산량을 감당해 낼 수 있습니다. 이는 가장 많이 사용하는 세 가지 사이즈를 다양하게 제공하여 드림으로써 타 회사와의 차별점을 확실히 느낄 수 있으실 것입니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-2425ba45-4cc8-488d-b5dc-2bab38732704\" style=\"color:#ff008c;\"><b>사이즈가 다양하다는 것은 고객의 선택의 폭이 넓다는 것이며 또한 각각의 사이즈를 따로따로 구매할 수 있는 경쟁력이 있다는 것</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4486f5e7-1d9f-4e32-aa13-b49f2d585664\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-71c78435-4798-491e-af7f-0e71561ee24f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fade39fd-02c8-4725-aa5d-595a76120e27\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5d6c98d7-b2b6-416e-b790-0592a3d21bfc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223073085794/011.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dda89ff2-6f87-472f-9337-1f7e86e5fb9a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e8b58e8e-4adc-4030-b771-38716fa4a2cd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-17ed148a-b32c-4011-b577-85dfaf2262a4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-40a1c6cc-759a-4380-82c8-4695d500f8f3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>그 밖의 다양한 기능</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-01819ae6-6154-41b7-bd8c-8a8ec71eb6a3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1432f2e9-2f8b-410f-87c1-81dae708511e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-84217063-f700-436b-99a5-cdd1b687c5fc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0b455ce4-2d4d-4932-9741-54add746a0df\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-42671983-dbc7-48b8-bb09-a51837a4250d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8a79d607-afa4-464e-bb1b-763b9b6bab87\" style=\"color:#555555;\">1. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b4f8f27c-ec3e-4449-a686-a362a345e526\" style=\"color:#00b976;\"><b>Hot/Ice와 동시에 사용이 가능</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-21f45e5f-c2c8-41f2-a0bc-e983fa5a0ad6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">합니다. 영하 -20도에서 120도까지 모두 자유롭게 사용이 가능합니다. 컵을 뜨거운 홀더 차가운 홀더를 구분하여 관리하는 것은 여간 번거로운 일이 아닙니다. 이는 컵과 홀더 사이에 공간을 두어 음료와 홀더 사이에 열전도율을 낮춰 두 기능 모두 가능하도록 설계하였기 때문입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4c9bbc7c-c39c-4a9d-b266-ce68cb9072ed\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a6c44f90-b4b1-493d-8b0d-93475793b33d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4a80bff4-620e-44f2-85fa-7970f07dd625\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f039b0ae-0f64-4f91-a33d-05011fe78213\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7e461e46-f28e-4122-ae7c-09a097d2ee02\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7dc5e6d0-e886-4c43-a9e6-85ee9274eba7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">2. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-0f20f8ce-3ba0-43b2-8e1d-e11b0a599239\" style=\"color:#00b976;\"><b>컵과 홀더의 일체형</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-df3bb687-496d-4823-97d1-8b92597879b5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">으로 보호용 홀더가 흘러내리지 않습니다. 주변을 감싸는 홀더가 컵 상단에 고정되어 있어 별도로 홀더를 구매하거나 홀더가 흘러내리는 것을 방지할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e350d9f2-5373-4c84-ba5c-2743431ea01f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b21fb5ce-7f82-45c4-af12-7c265dbe1f0a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-65e5dd0a-30d2-42ab-a13c-82457de17246\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-579641ca-4bf3-40f1-b26c-0cc9e1a49c34\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9d4d1056-e46d-4b78-ad24-aa598147b8bf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-977f9296-a61c-4f86-a24e-b5845aa85037\" style=\"color:#555555;\">3. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b63cf3cd-a6e1-47be-a47a-888fb8560cb8\" style=\"color:#00b976;\"><b>컵, 홀더, 뚜껑이 모두 단일 소재</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-659f87a0-1cbb-43a9-b2fe-809bc20d9a76\" style=\"color:#555555;\">로 되어 있어 있습니다. 우리가 분리수거를 하실 때는 생각해 보십시오. 모든 홀더 컵은 종이와 플라스틱을 별도로 분리하여 배출해야 합니다. 하지만 본 제품의 경우 배출 시 따로 분리해야 하는 번거로움을 해소할 수 있습니다. 가장 편리하게 뚜껑과 홀더, 컵을 한 번에 재활용 수거함에 배출하면 되는 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ca2e6325-90ad-4cc4-9b3a-c9a1bec3f97a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0f1230bb-4ac3-4329-9771-555943252321\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-12a12316-0080-41fe-a718-2ae7c8e351ab\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3d99deaa-0d9c-4760-bb4a-40537bb407d5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9dd27edb-6344-4211-8fcb-c1915a051844\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cab2e867-3ceb-4e63-b4c4-50cce639039a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">4. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-94807a50-371a-4e7f-8c8b-8603d057a1aa\" style=\"color:#00b976;\"><b>전자레인지/식기세척기 사용 가능</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a7bae161-f4c6-4be0-a07e-9f8393a2ff5f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 제품입니다. 세척이나 보관 또는 요리에도 사용이 가능하도록 제작된 제품입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7ffcf04c-3fd9-47de-b1d0-d548654ba9d5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0f87d25b-c5f6-4f6f-bd88-8ae122e7ec22\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-table se-l-default\" id=\"SE-33ca4a6f-f4c3-41e0-a35c-d8738d16cf29\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-table se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"se-table-container\">\n<table class=\"se-table-content\" style=\"border-style:dashed;border-width:1px 0px 0px 1px;border-color:#c2c2c2;\">\n<tbody><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 16.4%; height: 43.0px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; background-color: #e3fdc8;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-79805c65-b45e-4927-bb03-b643bb8861b1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-e4f6f9c3-9bd5-4af5-94d8-ec7ab7a1a441\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>구분</b></span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 41.8%; height: 43.0px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; background-color: #e3fdc8;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b6b4c997-8e55-4f00-af18-83198fbe87f2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-fb6257c5-a615-4380-9de3-aa7ff6bab447\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>Take-out cup</b></span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 41.8%; height: 43.0px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; background-color: #e3fdc8;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7478eccb-70ed-483f-a79f-41bb296a7ee0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-02b57814-6adc-452a-986e-07c5176f4efb\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>EMC Re-Usalbe cup</b></span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 16.4%; height: 10.75px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e5bc9f76-03e1-42e2-aeaa-4d2b31cf1eac\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1154dfeb-cf99-4bc3-aba6-15f7479cc932\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제품 소재</span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 41.8%; height: 10.75px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e4a77930-d021-4d1a-90f1-9a47e4e2e73c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aa2fc9ac-7c46-4ee4-8ea6-7f38629d4c92\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이, 코팅제(PE), PET, PS</span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 41.8%; height: 10.75px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-70794b63-e972-433a-b21a-344a28e5c0bd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7ec8bada-3184-4580-8ef5-0dcd2ee8784e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">폴리프로필렌(PP) / BPA FREE</span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 16.4%; height: 10.75px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bdf81727-d216-4c32-b56c-07d20535c836\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-31c2bbb5-c646-48cd-845b-349c4cc1a076\" style=\"color:#555555;\">내구성</span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 41.8%; height: 10.75px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-08cc0a58-d18e-42f7-9be9-00d90e748f3c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ff121052-dd8b-49da-a451-f36f6f98e7de\" style=\"color:#555555;\">· 쉽게 젖거나 변형이 쉬움</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1203b229-7509-4741-a2b0-7e4d695bf96a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9855c29a-a1d5-4f7a-a6ae-447a5315b1c5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">· PE(종이컵, 코팅제) : 105~110℃</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b5d5d400-085b-465d-8c85-c7494054df3c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d74b98ef-009e-4414-8dff-d86a3ceefe13\" style=\"color:#555555;\">· PS : 70~90℃</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0515a520-6c33-4ff5-9f18-03096d4af74a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-412fd5e9-6a27-44fb-a415-39306fa400de\" style=\"color:#555555;\">· PEeT : 60~150℃</span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 41.8%; height: 10.75px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ad252e69-67cd-42ce-a196-e056085a50bd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-14707235-96dc-432b-965e-e61c99d38e2c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">· 젖지 않고 전자레인지/식기세척기 가능</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-44594acb-f153-493a-ae0f-0f56b301afff\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-06553e4a-bb8d-41a7-ae12-c784cbe1e4de\" style=\"color:#555555;\">· PP : -20~120℃</span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 16.4%; height: 33.75px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c337ebce-d941-4aa0-bfd0-de3516789a9a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-482eab59-7e23-4d00-a395-34ff3b3a1201\" style=\"color:#555555;\">재사용</span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 41.8%; height: 33.75px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4d2cfa8d-373e-4842-9b2f-ea42ab610c80\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a140e800-f716-4391-8283-bc48fbfe7152\" style=\"color:#555555;\">불가</span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 41.8%; height: 33.75px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-25c36d60-c1a0-4467-82b2-300a54985923\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a81b984d-4d68-46f1-b773-a64c1b3a89fe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가능(반영구적)</span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 16.4%; height: 10.75px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e923ba6c-28f3-476a-9339-f84ddfc66649\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-16796464-72dc-4763-9448-dc4614c36d94\" style=\"color:#555555;\">재활용</span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 41.8%; height: 10.75px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8e8bbec5-0253-4be3-87e2-f768fab9b518\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-00eebfed-0e27-4774-ae9d-12edfafc1ea0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이컵의 코팅제를 벗기거나 뚜껑, 아이스 잔에 혼용되어 사용되는 PE, PS를 육안으로 분리배출하는 것이 쉽지 않습니다.</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cb295ce0-1180-4ef7-b6fc-3926912d15ae\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0af3c9b2-3783-4d7d-9362-6004f1e28833\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7ed0da1c-8d40-4940-b097-e6a7098f3b93\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-38cb287c-3f76-4ca4-ad2d-1621992cb8c2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">분리배출 뒤에도 재활용 업체의 추가 비용이 필수사항</span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 41.8%; height: 10.75px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5f8f1c1e-c061-4a0f-a6e4-9d6ecb5fd907\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b086490a-85a5-40e1-b686-ff021a358024\" style=\"color:#555555;\">핫 컵, 아이스 컵, 슬리브, 뚜껑까지 모두 단일 소재 PP로 제작되어 분리배출 및 재활용 용이</span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 16.4%; height: 10.75px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8bf4eb27-a1db-4bfe-b007-d5349920c983\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9d947533-d4b1-49d3-ae49-6513801e0981\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄</span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 41.8%; height: 10.75px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4ba55dda-fda8-4037-a635-5994fb950f9f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-671eeb57-db7f-441a-aabb-ff949037f0c5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">색상, 이미지 구현에 한계가 있습니다.</span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 41.8%; height: 10.75px; border-style:dashed;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#c2c2c2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f2d4e53c-9174-41a3-a211-cd87aea9bc04\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-50ecca44-75e9-44b0-952b-0c17e469e043\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고퀄리티 이미지 구현 가능(그라비아 10도 인쇄까지 가능)</span></p></div>\n</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-72ec0e9d-d88e-46a6-b9bf-c5fbe1a31c88\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-35fd7d0a-5e4d-414a-a8dd-e2db2add3f15\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-587154a8-2c6b-4df5-a8d2-8111d9f7c823\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a6a36202-183b-4c03-8e18-97ee1b59f9d5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:191px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223073085794/012.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-029f9d6c-8b52-4a03-8069-96e86edb70f5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f8775103-230a-4741-bbee-83386013d303\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0c7c7bdc-9fe3-4f8a-a8e8-b0f90689e085\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-4eab3c2e-4bbd-4b8a-ab8a-4937a159e389\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223073085794/013.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-912f68f2-dd73-48ae-a8c7-69042613e1ba\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ed280d01-c177-4cd9-acb7-cfe85952fbe1\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>자유로운 디자인을 별도로 제작할 수 있습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d2304bfa-9281-4a40-b71e-c1884e6cac9c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3b2f05bd-6d11-471a-9d08-de2b70022448\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자체 생산설비와 기술력으로 그라비아 10도 인쇄로 제작됩니다. 이는 특정한 색상으로만 단순하게 구현되는 컬러 체계를 벗어나 더 섬세하고 더 다양한 색상 구현이 가능함으로써 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-5895f535-82e0-4ee1-89b3-33a49efd6d8a\" style=\"color:#ff008c;\"><b>자신만의 브랜드와 시그니처 컬러를 자유롭게 제작, 생산</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0b1f448c-239a-4cf3-afd2-ffc4f7107671\" style=\"color:#555555;\">할 수 있다는 뜻입니다. 다양한 자신만의 디자인으로 여러 가지 형태의 굿즈를 제작해 보십시오. 여러분의 취향에 맞는 굿즈 제작에 도움이 되는 시스템으로 제공하여 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8c08c809-cd51-46e6-9b9e-bc995b5cf40f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-287d5768-a935-4514-b8a9-da922db87ffd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9085fe93-1ca0-4d89-a9ab-2a0a299eed12\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223073085794/014.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8501d37d-f267-432a-a525-16f068b2eb0c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0cab008a-9d92-4260-a2e4-0254d65b2a09\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-83929765-a6a3-4d2e-8682-9a272db3f006\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ecb381de-53f5-4ebf-8f5d-db931d951a52\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-21f1b7dd-0710-4f12-93a7-7f27b760da08\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a1ab5996-fcb8-4cf6-a501-9fd91cd342da\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-04bb51fa-7b61-405a-917f-26fe26789897\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>이런 분에게 필요합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e7ec06f8-83cf-4091-8d11-2854247d78d5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a8e66e38-8366-477f-b321-47ea9762111c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3c5a0856-99c6-41c0-b943-19831df93cff\" style=\"color:#555555;\">1. 각종 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-72bccd96-17a5-4821-91b2-3cb970e195ac\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#c2f4db;\"><b>팬클럽, 지자체 행사, 각종 모임에 자신만의 디자인이나 브랜드로 홍보</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-add6599f-2539-411a-b40c-f2dc24167277\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하면서 환경에 구애받지 않는 모범적인 사례를 만들고자 하는 단체나 기업</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0da757f4-312a-4646-8d59-75585c7c5426\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a527d830-8a1e-4dd5-963b-405278a02a72\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e314cf80-26a4-490c-8eee-8f5330c39175\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b6670592-e459-442b-aa95-de220b103f9c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">2. 환경 조성이나 지역 개발 조성 시에 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-855cfd8c-e0df-4e1e-ab00-59ab587c02ff\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#c2f4db;\"><b>모범적으로 지역 환경을 보호</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-60fea3ab-5949-4bfa-ab36-36e7fa7bd9fc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하고자 하는 지역 중심 카페나 각종 요식업 협회</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-29708bc8-c68c-474d-88a7-17102cab542d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b34584bb-f7e4-42dd-a031-8980ccbfc129\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9f4880f6-738a-429b-8140-8d679b5099a5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-13a6d67b-67b9-48ea-8906-1d31383dcbe3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">3. 개별적으로 자유롭게 디자인을 요청하여 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-aee5d3a1-4034-4b72-9053-b22604b7e00e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#c2f4db;\"><b>자신만의 브랜드를 홍보하고 싶은 판촉물 전문 기업</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9550797c-c982-48e6-a721-9126ffaf9068\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 딜러나 회사</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5aeb5aa0-b3e8-4714-b675-fa6e8b355834\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a854f277-9c5a-4e47-95b8-28151822f7bf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-1f425e36-7fec-4d0d-ba4f-6126803736b6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-faa2aef3-cea8-46e5-bb5c-5ed20b6b1db1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ff3bec2c-a8ac-4db7-ac58-28dc5dd33ffb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ece8513a-1922-42bd-8c1f-55a62b2c2341\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-88bc78ad-3fc7-4a55-bb2c-9ce9b7d3e8f9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}